    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo defines a new DNS RR type for experimental purposes.  This RFC describes a mechanism to allow the DNS to carry location information about hosts, networks, and subnets.  This memo defines an Experimental Protocol for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
